thread.title: Customer

author: Customer
title: Customer
text:
Great place, very knowledgeable musicians there to help guide you to make the right purchase. I have also returned a couple items because one was an item i didnt like and another was not the right thing i needed. Returned for cash back/money back to bank account.
Strongly contemplated getting an elektron rytm but decided against it after having the opportunity to play with one at the store... that could have been an expensive mistake.
